function_call.arguments: {"risks":[{"Description":"Close interaction and co-creation may lead to increased risk of contagious diseases transmission.","Impact":"Potential spread of contagious diseases among clients and practitioners, leading to illness or outbreaks.","Mitigation":"Implement strict hygiene protocols, use of personal protective equipment, and maintain social distancing measures during interactions.","Technologies":"Use of contactless technologies for virtual interactions, digital transactions, and remote consultations.","People":"Nutritionists, real estate partners, clients, families with small children, medical professionals, clinic staff, government officials, patients.","Owner":"Individual practitioners, service providers, organizations, government authorities, technology developers."}]}
